"7:65:7" : {s: 7, a: 65, w: 7, r: "عبد", t: "ٱعْبُدُوا۟", l: "عَبَدَ", lc: 122, tl: "uʿ'budū", lb: "উপাসনা করা ",e: "Worship", b: "তোমরা এবাদত কর", f: 17, rm: "serve, worship, adore, venerate, accept the impression of a thing, obey with submissiveness or humility, approve, apply, devote, obedience, slave, keep to inseparably, subdue, assemble together, enslave."},
